description: Atlanta’s newest food truck, Ibiza Bites, offers a brand new style of cuisine it calls “SoLa” -- a little bit South American, a little bit Latin American, a little deep South and a whole lot of delicious. Ibiza Bites is the ﬁrst collaboration from Dennis Dean Dining Concepts, an affiliate of DENNIS DEAN / a catering company, named of one Atlanta’s Top 20 Caterers by the Atlanta Business Chronicle’s Hospitality Quarterly and a former “Best of Atlanta Caterer” by Creative Loaﬁng.
name: Ibiza Bites
